Job Details
National General Insurance associate of ENBD bank is looking out for UNIT MANAGERS to develop Life Insurance department .Ideally candidate with Life insurance experience in UAE preferred alternatively sales experience (out door ) of minimum 2 years is acceptable .Must have capacity of networking skills to develop team and drive business targets . Graduation must. Age minimum 35 years with driving license (UAE) desirable.
Requirements
